. Running the Application
To run the application locally:

Install the dependencies:

 
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run the API server:

python app.py


Test the API using Postman or cURL. For example, to create a rule:

bash

curl -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"rule": "age > 30 AND department = \'Sales\'"}' http://localhost:5000/create_rule
